<doc id="1330395" wikidata="Q1038124" url="?curid=1330395" title="Home Free (Dan Fogelberg album)">
<text>Home Free is the debut album by American singer-songwriter Dan Fogelberg, released in 1972. Upon its original release, &quot;Home Free&quot; had lukewarm success, but following a later reissue, it was certified platinum by the RIAA for certified sales of 1,000,000 copies.

