* Mixed by John Stronach at Record Plant (Sausalito, CA).
* Mastered by Rick Collins at Kendun Recorders (Burbank, CA).
* Design – Ron Coro
* Photography – Henry Diltz
* Cover Artwork – Dan Fogelberg

