<doc id="1330484" wikidata="Q2681104" url="?curid=1330484" title="Nether Lands">
<text>Nether Lands is the fourth album by American singer-songwriter Dan Fogelberg, released in 1977. The album title is a play on Nederland, Colorado, the location of one of the studios used to record the album.

==Track listing==
All songs written by Dan Fogelberg.
