#&quot;Love Gone By&quot; – 3:04
#&quot;Promises Made&quot; – 3:18
#&quot;Give Me Some Time&quot; – 3:20
#&quot;Scarecrow&#x27;s Dream&quot; For Don Quixote, Walt Disney and the Wizard of Oz – 4:10
#&quot;Sketches&quot; – 3:32
#&quot;False Faces&quot; – 4:52

